entry.content: Replying to @Elsie | Tech | Foodie bey hun you to fix your Diet: Focus on whole foods; avoid processed foods. Strength Training: Build muscle to boost metabolism. Cardio: Helps burn extra calories. Consistency: Keep up with regular workouts. Sleep: Aim for 7-9 hours nightly. Stress: Manage it, as high levels can hinder weight loss. Hydration: Drink lots of water. Measure Progress: Use photos, clothes fit, and not just the scale. Stay Positive: Results can take time; stay patient.
